Comment: 10,0:06:19.57,0:06:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a good time. Wagandea will soon\Nopen its buds and release its pollen.
Comment: 10,0:06:24.69,0:06:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The pollen contains a potent toxin. If a witch comes into contact with it, she will lose something forever. {there are other ways to put it, but length}
Comment: 10,0:06:29.83,0:06:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Lose something forever?
Comment: 10,0:06:32.93,0:06:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you would have wanted to go\Nright away if I had told you, so I kept it a secret.
