Comment: 10,0:06:47.30,0:06:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,A few weeks on the shorter end{ of the scale/range},\Nbut it's a few months on the longer.
Comment: 10,0:06:52.12,0:06:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,In some exceedingly rare cases, it could potentially be around for several years.{pollen takes 'it'}
