Comment: 10,0:10:05.64,0:10:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Once they are all gathered, \Nthe Grand Triskelion will be released.{## is "released" consistent with the idea of the triskelion? i was thinking of it being sealed, so maybe "unsealed"...?}{when they use different words in Japanese, so do I}
Comment: 10,0:10:09.30,0:10:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What will you wish for when you obtain the power of world reconstruction magic?
Comment: 10,0:10:16.10,0:10:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um, to be honest, I'm not really all that good at thinking about difficult things.
Comment: 10,0:10:20.91,0:10:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Comment: 0,0:10:21.07,0:10:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1}Ồ?
Comment: 10,0:10:22.05,0:10:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,My biggest reason for chasing after the Words is really just to meet Chariot.
Comment: 10,0:10:26.41,0:10:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to meet Chariot?
Comment: 10,0:10:28.63,0:10:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like as long as I keep finding the Words,\NI'll get to meet her eventually.
Comment: 10,0:10:33.34,0:10:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You like her that much?
Comment: 10,0:10:35.28,0:10:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! There's so much I want to ask and tell Chariot once I meet her!
Comment: 10,0:10:40.33,0:10:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}And the very first thing I'll do is thank her!
Comment: 10,0:10:43.11,0:10:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I see.
Comment: 10,0:10:45.11,0:10:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Don't worry.
Comment: 10,0:10:46.50,0:10:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you'll meet her soon.
Comment: 10,0:10:48.48,0:10:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Comment: 10,0:10:50.09,0:10:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}For sure...{## can go either way but i think this is too ominous to be said out loud}
Comment: 10,0:10:58.42,0:11:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,As I expected, we still have time before the buds open.
Comment: 10,0:11:02.48,0:11:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Comment: 10,0:11:03.60,0:11:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yay!
Comment: 10,0:11:05.05,0:11:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}But that makes it all the stranger.
Comment: 0,0:11:06.62,0:11:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1}Sao cơ?
Comment: 10,0:11:06.81,0:11:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Huh?
Comment: 10,0:11:07.56,0:11:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Why would Professor Ursula try to stop you\Nwithout checking it first herself?
Comment: 10,0:11:12.34,0:11:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Because...
Comment: 10,0:11:13.78,0:11:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Perhaps there was some sort of reason why she wanted to prevent you from climbing it.
Comment: 10,0:11:18.54,0:11:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,There are some things about her I'm suspicious of.
Comment: 10,0:11:22.25,0:11:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Comment: 10,0:11:24.07,0:11:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,She says she was classmates with Chariot,
Comment: 10,0:11:27.15,0:11:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,but I have no recollection of a student named "Ursula".{I was legitamately going to fix this when I saw it during editing, so gj}
Comment: 10,0:11:32.19,0:11:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It must be because she didn't leave much of an impression! Not everyone can stand out like Chariot.
Comment: 10,0:11:37.18,0:11:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That may be the case.{## notion of "reason" is reserved already}
Comment: 10,0:11:39.60,0:11:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Either way...
Comment: 10,0:11:42.00,0:11:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be wary of her.
Comment: 10,0:11:44.03,0:11:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Comment: 0,0:11:44.12,0:11:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1}Sao cơ?
Comment: 10,0:11:45.47,0:11:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,She might be hiding something from you.
Comment: 10,0:11:48.82,0:11:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Something {\fax-0.2}very{\i0} important.
Comment: 10,0:11:51.45,0:11:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,She was just worried because\Nof how dangerous it is here!
Comment: 10,0:11:54.86,0:11:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm always doing stupid things.
Comment: 10,0:11:58.98,0:12:05.24,Default,,15,15,0,,You'll need to climb under your own power without using any tools or magic if you want to learn the Word.
Comment: 10,0:12:05.24,0:12:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you prepared to do that?
Comment: 10,0:12:08.03,0:12:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I am. I swear I'll make it up.
Comment: 10,0:12:31.24,0:12:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Akko...
Comment: 10,0:12:32.35,0:12:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you there?
Comment: 10,0:12:38.15,0:12:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Croix!
Comment: 10,0:12:43.90,0:12:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This brings back memories.
Comment: 10,0:12:47.95,0:12:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember, Chariot?
Comment: 10,0:12:50.14,0:12:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Back when we first came to this forest.
Comment: 10,0:12:53.71,0:12:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember it all too clearly.
Comment: 10,0:12:56.46,0:12:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I will never be able to forget.
Comment: 10,0:12:59.54,0:13:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}I swear upon the Nine Olde Witches!
Comment: 10,0:13:01.83,0:13:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}One day, I will release the seal on the ultimate magic!
Comment: 10,0:13:05.34,0:13:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}I'll become the world's greatest witch!
Comment: 10,0:13:08.10,0:13:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}I also swear it!
Comment: 10,0:13:09.72,0:13:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}I want to bring fun to all.
Comment: 10,0:13:11.63,0:13:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}I want to make everyone in the world forget their sadness and hatred with a smile!
Comment: 0,0:13:35.28,0:13:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1}Ồ... cái gì thế này?
Comment: 10,0:13:36.79,0:13:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}It can't be...
Comment: 10,0:13:41.15,0:13:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}The time has come once more for the staff of seven stars to choose a master. {there's stuff about "in a very long time" too}{## can you check if we had capital letters for staff of seven stars somewhere? "The Staff of the Seven Stars" or something? i'm running out of time}{we hadn't had caps}
Comment: 10,0:13:46.05,0:13:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}It chose Chariot?
Comment: 10,0:13:48.30,0:13:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}Why not me?!
Comment: 10,0:13:49.69,0:13:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}Chariot, you must revive the seven Words with that staff.
Comment: 10,0:13:55.98,0:13:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}No...
Comment: 10,0:14:02.78,0:14:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Croix!
Comment: 10,0:14:05.07,0:14:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't stop me!
Comment: 10,0:14:11.53,0:14:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You're scared, Croix.
Comment: 10,0:14:14.86,0:14:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You're scared of Akko getting her hands on the Grand Triskelion.
Comment: 10,0:14:19.57,0:14:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Scared?
Comment: 10,0:14:21.09,0:14:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You might be able to knock Akko off course,\Nbut you can't get the Grand Triskelion.{## make akko lose her way but enough with the memes; also, was this otoshimeru?}{it is}
Comment: 10,0:14:25.30,0:14:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You should understand that!
Comment: 10,0:14:29.01,0:14:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}She hasn't got the slightest clue about what it means to obtain the Grand Triskelion.
Comment: 10,0:14:33.99,0:14:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The staff erred in choosing its owner, just as it did before.
Comment: 10,0:14:39.14,0:14:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, not that it matters.
Comment: 10,0:14:41.07,0:14:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no more need for that staff. {don't wanna be too}
Comment: 0,0:14:43.90,0:14:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1}Cái gì?
Comment: 10,0:14:45.63,0:14:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Do you want to know why I don't simply leave her alone?
Comment: 10,0:14:48.61,0:14:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}It's because she is your last hope of a dream.{## anything cooler for "final dream"? ultimate dream? dream of all dreams? not convinced by any of them so i didn't edit it in, just thinking}{hopefully this}
Comment: 10,0:15:19.96,0:15:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}I won't give up...{## you can hear her breathe}
Comment: 10,0:15:21.49,0:15:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}I swear... I'll climb all the way up!
Comment: 10,0:15:37.72,0:15:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Comment: 10,0:15:44.88,0:15:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor!
Comment: 10,0:15:50.13,0:15:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back, Akko!
Comment: 10,0:15:51.85,0:15:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry, grab on!
Comment: 10,0:15:53.59,0:15:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Comment: 10,0:15:55.89,0:15:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I made it this far already! You were wrong!
Comment: 10,0:15:59.48,0:16:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor Croix told me the pollen is still fine!
Comment: 10,0:16:02.56,0:16:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}No, I'm telling the truth!
Comment: 10,0:16:04.60,0:16:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The flowers above us are already opening! You can't go on!
Comment: 10,0:16:08.15,0:16:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying that Professor Croix lied to me?
Comment: 10,0:16:11.51,0:16:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know what she's really like. Turn back, Akko!
Comment: 10,0:16:15.10,0:16:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw it myself! The buds are shut tight!
Comment: 10,0:16:18.36,0:16:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The pollen isn't going anywhere!
Comment: 10,0:16:19.87,0:16:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Akko, please!
Comment: 10,0:16:21.49,0:16:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why won't you let me go?!
Comment: 0,0:16:23.02,0:16:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1}Sao cơ?
Comment: 10,0:16:24.75,0:16:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You don't understand how desperately\NI want to meet Chariot!
Comment: 10,0:16:29.88,0:16:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I don't care about the Words.\NI just want to meet Chariot!
Comment: 10,0:16:33.66,0:16:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}That's why I've done what you said\Nand collected all the Words!
Comment: 10,0:16:37.48,0:16:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}So why now?!
Comment: 10,0:16:39.01,0:16:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you telling me to stop?!
Comment: 10,0:16:42.50,0:16:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Akko.
Comment: 10,0:16:47.19,0:16:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Croix!
Comment: 10,0:16:48.02,0:16:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll convince Professor Ursula.
Comment: 10,0:16:51.78,0:16:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and go.
Comment: 10,0:16:53.16,0:16:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Professor Croix.
Comment: 10,0:16:55.11,0:16:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Akko!
Comment: 10,0:16:57.32,0:16:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Croix, move!
Comment: 10,0:16:58.95,0:17:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I can do that.
Comment: 10,0:17:01.09,0:17:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not going anywhere.{## "i won't let you" doesn't work with "croix, move!"}
Comment: 10,0:17:05.25,0:17:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Give up already!
Comment: 10,0:17:28.77,0:17:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}Chariot! Wake up, Chariot!
Comment: 10,0:17:33.52,0:17:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}Croix...
Comment: 10,0:17:35.03,0:17:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}Chariot...
Comment: 10,0:17:36.24,0:17:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Chariot!
Comment: 10,0:17:49.66,0:17:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The pollen will be released in only a moment.
Comment: 10,0:17:52.50,0:17:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll never make it in time.
Comment: 10,0:17:55.52,0:17:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it up.
Comment: 10,0:17:58.05,0:18:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll protect Akko.
Comment: 10,0:18:03.39,0:18:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No way...
Comment: 10,0:18:06.92,0:18:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough!
Comment: 10,0:18:15.07,0:18:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}I won't lose.
Comment: 10,0:18:17.83,0:18:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}I'm going to meet Chariot!
Comment: 10,0:18:20.54,0:18:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}I'll become a witch like Chariot!
Comment: 10,0:18:35.63,0:18:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go.
Comment: 10,0:18:51.86,0:18:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The pollen!
Comment: 10,0:18:53.69,0:18:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Comment: 10,0:19:06.98,0:19:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}It's all over...
Comment: 10,0:19:11.16,0:19:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Akko!
Comment: 10,0:19:15.17,0:19:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}I'm begging you... please don't steal her future!
Comment: 10,0:19:45.44,0:19:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor Ursula?!
Comment: 10,0:19:49.58,0:19:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Akko...
Comment: 10,0:19:51.15,0:19:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you hurt?
Comment: 10,0:19:52.68,0:19:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor, I'm so sorry...
Comment: 10,0:19:55.43,0:19:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I said such horrible things to you...
Comment: 10,0:19:59.52,0:20:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But you still saved me...
Comment: 10,0:20:03.63,0:20:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}I'm sorry...
Comment: 10,0:20:05.88,0:20:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}I'm so sorry...
Comment: 10,0:20:07.30,0:20:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}Croix...
Comment: 10,0:20:08.60,0:20:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}Not me...
Comment: 10,0:20:10.43,0:20:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}It was... it was supposed to be you...
Comment: 10,0:20:13.31,0:20:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}Why did I...
Comment: 10,0:20:20.14,0:20:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2\an8}Accept it, Chariot.
Comment: 10,0:20:22.36,0:20:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2\an8}You were entrusted with it.
Comment: 10,0:20:25.25,0:20:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}You'll be the one to get the Grand Triskelion.
Comment: 10,0:20:40.67,0:20:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who needs to apologize.
Comment: 10,0:20:43.15,0:20:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I might've just been pushing my wish onto you.{why do I always fuck this up}
Comment: 10,0:20:48.11,0:20:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't thinking about your true feelings at all.
Comment: 10,0:20:51.39,0:20:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true! You didn't force me to do anything!
Comment: 10,0:20:54.23,0:20:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}It was my own decision to gather the Words.
Comment: 10,0:20:57.05,0:21:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I've gone through so much, and experienced so many things, but I haven't grown one bit!
Comment: 10,0:21:02.52,0:21:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I never meant to say that to you!
Comment: 10,0:21:05.20,0:21:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You've always come to my rescue,\Nalways been there for me, so I... {it's really hard to type through the tears and shaking fingers}
Comment: 10,0:21:11.32,0:21:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}What I really wanted to say was...
Comment: 10,0:21:14.79,0:21:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Comment: 10,0:21:21.26,0:21:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Lyonne.
Comment: 10,0:21:25.68,0:21:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it... that's what Lyonne means.
Comment: 10,0:21:30.13,0:21:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}Accept it, Chariot.
Comment: 10,0:21:32.32,0:21:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}You were entrusted with it.
Comment: 10,0:21:37.32,0:21:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2\fad(0,1602)}Lyonne.
Comment: 10,0:21:54.14,0:21:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a single person has ever seen the top of Wagandea.
Comment: 10,0:21:58.03,0:22:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Wagandea has no end.
Comment: 10,0:22:02.23,0:22:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Akko.
Comment: 10,0:22:04.56,0:22:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You've grown so much.
Comment: 10,0:22:14.28,0:22:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}I have no need for the Shiny Rod or the seven Words.
Comment: 10,0:22:19.88,0:22:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}I will use the most forceful method I can think of, take the seal on the Grand Triskelion...
Comment: 10,0:22:27.20,0:22:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}And break it.
Comment: 10,0:21:37.32,0:21:38.94,Default - Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(1602,0)}Lyonne.
